title.rendered: Alticor Inc Wins ASSE Large Contractor Award

content.rendered: Alticor Inc’ Pacific District was recently awarded first place in the Large Contractor category at the 14th Biennial Governor’s Pacific Rim Safety and Health Conference. This award was presented by American Society of Safety Engineers (ASSE) President Michael Belcher and is recognized by both the Hawaii Occupational Safety and Health Division (HIOSH) and ASSE. Brad Jeanneret, Vice President, and Adam Cotton, Director of Safety and Health, accepted this prestigious award on behalf of the Pacific District.
